542
00:40:56,260 --> 00:41:00,640
I am... your Mrs. Tang.

543
00:41:03,700 --> 00:41:05,330
Wife,

544
00:41:07,770 --> 00:41:09,510
I love you.

545
00:41:13,720 --> 00:41:18,440
Husband, I also love you very much.

